                		           <p class="aamTagLine">Its about your life and your journey!</p>         
                    </span>
                	</div>
                	
                	<div> 
                  	   <img src="assets/booklet/parents.jpg" class="phdImage"/>
                    		<span class="bookletText">
                    		  <p>“Being the single child, my aging parents held me back from thinking ahead. I am looking for a guy who will take care of not just me, my parents too"</p>                      
                        </span>
                  </div>

                  <div>
                  	  <div class="headerText">What AapAurMain Believes</div>
                  		<span class="bookletText aamText pushTop">
                  		  <p>Our members believe marriage is an equilibrium, where both partners mutually share the ups and downs.</p>
                  		           <p class="aamTagLine">We ask you upfront about the deciding factors in your life so you do not waste time and emotions discovering them later!</p>         
                      </span>
                  </div>
                  	
                  	<!--Last page-->
                  <div> 
                    <img src="assets/booklet/together.jpg" class="phdImage"/>
                    
                    <span class="bookletText">
                      <p style="padding:40px">Your Life,Your Choice! </p>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                      	
                  <div>
                		<span class="bookletText aamText lastpageText">
                		  <p><h2 style="color:brown">The Beginning...</h2></p>
                		  <span class="bookletText aamText"><p>Write your amazing chapter here.</p></span>       
                    </span>
                  </div>
                	
                	
                </div> <!--mybook-->
      </div><!--book_wrapper-->
      </div><!-- Main talking area container ends -->
      <div class="faqs">
        <h2 class="faqHeader">
          <div class="faqText">
            Something you must know about us &hellip;
          </div>
        </h2>
        <div class="faqWrapper">
          <div class="leftCol">
            
            <div class="q">
              <div class="question">What We Are ?</div>
                <ul class="whatWeAre">
                  <li>Our members believe marriage is a union.Transaction in any form is unacceptable.</li>
                  <li>We ask for crisp details on things related to your preferences, opinions and aspirations only. Integrity and honesty are the aspects to look out for!.</li>
                  <li>The people you trust may make your profile; but we encourage you to create, discuss and choose for yourself as you understand your priorities best</li>
                  <li>We handpick matches through our extremely sophisticated and detailed understanding of you and your profile. Quality is the determining criterion</li>
                  
                </ul>
                </div>
          </div> <!-- div.leftCol -->
        
          <div class="rightCol">
            
            <div class="q">
              <div class="question">What we are not?</div>
              <ul class="whatWeAre">
                <li>We do not call ourselves a ‘serious’ dating site.. In fact, we are not even a dating site. </li>
                <li>We do not provide matches based on caste / race / religion / skin color / height and weight. We do not enquire about these details either.</li>
                <li>We do not flood our users with countless matches. We give you only a select few matches per week.</li>
                <li>We do not stand for multiple courtships. Loyalty in whatever we do is what defines our community. We do not provide further matches to a couple when they are getting to know each other</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
   
            
          </div> <!-- div.rightCol -->
      </div>
    </div> <!-- div.container -->
